textBox.richText: Jane had an end-of-season treat...6” of fresh snow for closing day. I had the summer storage wax on the S7s, so I scraped it off, and headed out. Funny, this is the way the resort was *supposed* to look all year long. We went down for the party in the C-Lot...Alli dressed up as Jane, and Max made a robot costume. Alli and Max wanted to hang out in the lot, so I ran up and got early tracks. Headed straight for Pano, but they had Animal Control up there to take care of some Moose! (That lift never did open). Did a bunch of trees instead...was the first one through the backside switchyard trees.
